OL,3,CCompany fined #240,000 after fall left
OL,4,Cman paralysed after 30ft fall at work
OL,6,FAn electrical transmission company has
OL,7,Fbeen fined #240,000 after a man was
OL,8,Fleft paralysed from the chest down
OL,9,Fafter a fall at work.
OL,11,FGavin Pugh, from Bangor, was 35 at the
OL,12,Ftime of the incident and employed as a
OL,13,Flinesman by Wood Transmission and
OL,14,FDistribution Limited.
OL,16,FHe had been demolishing and replacing
OL,17,Felectricity pylons in East
OL,18,FStaffordshire when he fell more than
OL,19,F30 feet on 6 April 2022.
