OL,3,CCompany fined #240,000 after fall left
OL,4,Cman paralysed after 30ft fall at work
OL,6,FThe team that was sent to the site
OL,7,Fthat day was also under-staffed for
OL,8,Fthe work being carried out.
OL,10,FAs the job progressed, Mr Pugh
OL,11,Funknowingly attached his fall
OL,12,Fprotection lanyard to a diagonal steel
OL,13,Fsection that was only securely bolted
OL,14,Fin place at its uppermost fixing.
OL,16,FAs he moved around the tower, the
OL,17,Fsteel section he was attached to
OL,18,Fdropped into a vertical position,
OL,19,Fcausing his lanyard to fall loose,
OL,20,Fresulting in him falling to the ground.
