OL,3,CCompany fined #240,000 after fall left
OL,4,Cman paralysed after 30ft fall at work
OL,6,FEarlier this year, Wood Transmission
OL,7,Fand Distribution Limited pleaded
OL,8,Fguilty at Birmingham Magistrates Court
OL,9,Fto breaching regulation 4(1) of the
OL,10,FWork at Height Regulation 2005.
OL,12,FAt a hearing on 17 July they were
OL,13,Fsubsequently fined #240,000 and
OL,14,Fordered to pay costs of #14,142.
OL,16,FHSE Inspector Robert Gidman said:
OL,17,F"This tragic incident could have been
OL,18,Fprevented had Wood Transmission and
OL,19,FDistribution Limited put in place
OL,20,Fadequate arrangements to protect its
OL,21,Fworkers from harm.
